nhc_headline: ...NARDA STRENGTHENS SOME MORE AND HEADING WESTWARD AWAY FROM MEXICO...
summary: ...NARDA STRENGTHENS SOME MORE AND HEADING WESTWARD AWAY FROM MEXICO... As of 9:00 PM CST Mon Sep 22 the center of Narda was located near 15.9, -105.1 with movement W at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 993 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
